            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Philada.</placeName>
                <date>April 23<hi rend="sup">rd</hi>. 1854</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>A Hart Esq</addressee> Parnass</p>
            <p>Kaal Kadosh Mickve Israel</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Sir       The undersigned members<lb/> of the “K K M I”, do
                respectfully request you to call a<lb/> special meeting of the members of the
                Congregation on the<lb/>
                <date>30th</date> Inst “for the purpose of approving the action of the<lb/> Board of
                Adjunta in repealing the vote of Censure passed<lb/> on the <persName>Revd. Isaac
                    Leeser</persName>, and for the further purpose of<lb/> passing suitable
                resolutions &amp; making a suitable appro=<lb/>=priation in his favor in part
                    <sic>acknowledgement</sic> of his<lb/> past services to said Congregation &amp;
                to assist him in<lb/> any future enterprise.”</p>
